  "key_observations_html": "<div style=\"border:1px solid #C7D8E8;border-radius:10px;padding:0.75rem 0.95rem;margin:0.1rem 0 0.55rem;background:#ffffff;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);\"><ul style=\"margin:0.1rem 0 0 1.05rem;padding:0;color:#1F4C67;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.45;\"><li><strong>TMMFs are becoming a de facto settlement layer for institutions:</strong> several of the largest funds combine very high AUM with small holder counts\u2014e.g. USYC (44 holders, $2.96B; ~$67M/holder), iBENJI (28 holders, $1.59B; ~$57M/holder), JTRSY (19 holders, $871M; ~$46M/holder)\u2014suggesting on-chain cash and collateral rails rather than broad retail savings products. Ethereum still carries ~52% of aggregated MMF network share, alongside selective deployment on chains used for institutional workflows.</li><li><strong>Early &quot;flight to efficiency&quot; shows up in 30D network share:</strong> gainers include Stellar (+2.46 pp 30D share), Solana (+2.37 pp 30D share); losers include BNB Chain (-4.35 pp 30D share), Ethereum (-2.31 pp 30D share). That pattern is consistent with liquidity migrating toward higher-throughput, lower-fee chains\u2014though Ethereum still dominates levels in most snapshots.</li><li><strong>Industry headlines emphasize Issuer strategy split</strong> Recent coverage includes <a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2026/06/02/galaxy-enters-institutional-prediction-markets-with-usd10-million-arca-trade\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Galaxy enters institutional prediction markets with $10 million Arca trade</a> (CoinDesk); <a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/kaiko-acquires-amberdata-blockchain-data-consolidation?utm_source=rss_feed&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=rss_partner_inbound\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kaiko acquires Amberdata in blockchain data consolidation push</a> (CoinTelegraph). Issuer strategy coverage can clarify whether the market is bifurcating into institutional rails vs retail yield products\u2014holder counts and AUM per holder in the funds table help validate that split.</li><li><strong>Industry headlines emphasize Chain efficiency &amp; migration</strong> Recent coverage includes <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Best Crypto To Buy Today? Strive Expands $4.2B Bitcoin Strategy As APEMARS Raises Over $500K Alongside Solana And Ethereum - StreetInsider</a> (Google News (digital assets)); <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiV0FVX3lxTFBQNllMbjctZHdvQWZQa2VWcTFvUXVTR0hoaXZZX2E3aEpTdTBZcHE2OVZjX3V2QXM0RXBmdVp5WV9NQm1HbEpraEo2bGVCM2liVFJER0E1Zw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Charles Schwab debuts 24/7 Bitcoin, Ether, Solana and Ripple futures, targets spot crypto for advisors next year - Cryptonews.net</a> (Google News (digital assets)). Fee and throughput narratives frequently foreshadow 30D network-share migration among tokenized funds\u2014check whether gainers in the By network table match the chains named in coverage.</li><li><strong>Industry headlines emphasize Regulation &amp; compliance</strong> Recent coverage includes <a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/zama-tightens-compliance-framework-after-court-ordered-usdc-freeze-reversed?utm_source=rss_feed&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=rss_partner_inbound\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zama accelerates compliance after court lifts $12.5M USDC freeze</a> (CoinTelegraph); <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMioAFBVV95cUxQWXo1aHNNdm9qR1dWeUJnYWVKNUlESkpvbGE3cnBkenI5U2hTbktwQzM4eUNLYWxFTXRKVFFZYTI3Q2VzRklfYXlFeGtJd092RnRwcG5BaEJpM0RaZXk4VWNQSng4ay16TTNSbnlINTR1VUhvcm5xTWVOaHpxVjU1YlhXM0JwMU1uMWdOY3RKYlY1WE4zWDdCUnFnRHFhYjd6?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BeInCrypto Institutional 100: Top 16 Names Shaping Digital Asset Regulation and Governance - BeInCrypto</a> (Google News (digital assets)). Cross-border compliance stories often explain why similar funds sit under different regulatory labels\u2014jurisdiction and investor-eligibility columns on this page are the practical read-through.</li></ul><p class=\"takeaways__note\">Context only\u2014not investment advice. Observations rank fund-level and network aggregates on this page against recent tokenization and money-market headlines. Bullets are ranked from on-page data and recent industry headlines (dashboard RSS plus Google News fallback).</p></div><p class=\"review-note ko-disclaimer\">Key observations are AI generated and should be reviewed for accuracy.</p>",
